<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><span style=3D"text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Instructions to the =
NSO participants</strong></span><strong>:</strong></p>
<p>1.&nbsp;&nbsp; They should attend the selection with <strong>proper spor=
tswear</strong>. (Other dress
<strong>i.e. Shirt, Pant,&nbsp;</strong><strong style=3D"font-size: 12pt;">=
Bermuda&#8217;s etc. is not allowed</strong><span style=3D"font-size: 12pt;=
">).</span></p>
<p>2.&nbsp;&nbsp; Do not bring valuable things (i.e. Cell phone, Gold ornam=
ents, Cash, Debit / ATM card etc.)</p>
<p>3.&nbsp;&nbsp; The selection <strong>results will be announced on the sa=
me day</strong> as soon as the programme is over.</p>
<p>4.&nbsp;&nbsp; A students can participate in as many sports she/he wants=
, until <strong>
she/he gets first two selections only.</strong></p>
<p>5.&nbsp;&nbsp; The NSO selection of results will be displayed on all the=
 Hostel notice board (tentatively).</p>
<p>6.&nbsp;&nbsp; Allocation to his/her chosen in sports will be done only =
if minimum number of student in all&nbsp;<span style=3D"font-size: 12pt;">s=
port is satisfied.</span></p>
<p>7.&nbsp;&nbsp; <strong>Medically unfit students are not eligible to unde=
rgo NSO programme</strong>.
